The '''1902 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their twelfth ever season of organized football. VMI went 3-3-1 in what would be [[Sam Walker (American football)|Sam Walker]] last season as VMI head coach.<ref name="VMI">http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf</ref>
